<item>
            <title>[LU-15793] kernel update [RHEL8.5 4.18.0-348.23.1.el8_5]</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15793</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Security Fix(es):&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: use-after-free in RDMA listen() (CVE-2021-4028)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: heap out of bounds write in nf_dup_netdev.c (CVE-2022-25636)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Bug Fix(es):&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Backport DFS fixes from upstream (BZ#2056329)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;RHEL8.5&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; lpfc driver often fails to detect storage directly connected to Broadcom FC HBA (BZ#2058193)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;nf_reinject calls nf_queue_entry_free on an already freed entry-&amp;gt;state (BZ#2061446)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;gfs2 blocking in gdlm_lock (BZ#2069750)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://access.redhat.com/errata/RHSA-2022:1550?sc_cid=701600000006NHXAA2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://access.redhat.com/errata/RHSA-2022:1550?sc_cid=701600000006NHXAA2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
